    "Deepglot combines low-cost LLMs with optional premium providers while your data stays under your control.": "Nascann Deepglot LLManna ar chostas íseal le soláthraithe préimhe roghnacha fad a fhanann do shonraí faoi do smacht.",
    "Deepglot currently uses your Gravatar. Direct uploads are not available yet.": "Úsáideann Deepglot do Gravatar faoi láthair. Níl uaslódálacha díreacha ar fáil go fóill.",
    "Deepglot gives you control over your translations again, with professional features at fair prices.": "Tugann Deepglot smacht duit ar do chuid aistriúcháin arís, le gnéithe gairmiúla ar phraghsanna cothroma.",
    "Deepglot provides software features for website translation, project management, and WordPress integration.": "Soláthraíonn Deepglot gnéithe bogearraí le haghaidh aistriúchán láithreán gréasáin, bainistíocht tionscadail agus comhtháthú WordPress.",
    "Deepglot signs every delivery with a timestamp and HMAC signature.": "Síníonn Deepglot gach seachadadh le stampa ama agus síniú HMAC.",
    "Deepglot support is available Monday to Friday from 9 a.m. to 5 p.m.": "Tá tacaíocht Deepglot ar fáil ó Luan go hAoine ó 9 r.n. go 5 i.n.",
    "Deepglot translates your WordPress content automatically with AI at a fraction of the usual cost. Your translations stay yours.": "Aistríonn Deepglot d’ábhar WordPress go huathoibríoch le AI ar chodán den ghnáthchostas. Is leatsa na haistriúcháin.",
    "Deepglot will continue to send important account, security, and project emails. Optional notification controls will appear once they can be persisted.": "Leanfaidh Deepglot ag seoladh ríomhphoist thábhachtacha chuntais, slándála agus tionscadail. Beidh rialuithe fógartha roghnacha le feiceáil a luaithe is féidir iad a leanúint.",
    "DeepL translation API. No model id is needed.": "API aistriúcháin DeepL. Níl aon samhail aitheantais ag teastáil.",
