    "Deepglot combines low-cost LLMs with optional premium providers while your data stays under your control.": "Deepglot jgħaqqad LLMs bi prezz baxx ma' fornituri ta' premium fakultattivi filwaqt li d-dejta tiegħek tibqa' taħt il-kontroll tiegħek.",
    "Deepglot currently uses your Gravatar. Direct uploads are not available yet.": "Deepglot bħalissa juża Gravatar tiegħek. It-uploads diretti għadhom mhumiex disponibbli.",
    "Deepglot gives you control over your translations again, with professional features at fair prices.": "Deepglot jerġa' jagħtik kontroll fuq it-traduzzjonijiet tiegħek, b'karatteristiċi professjonali bi prezzijiet ġusti.",
    "Deepglot provides software features for website translation, project management, and WordPress integration.": "Deepglot jipprovdi karatteristiċi tas-softwer għat-traduzzjoni tal-websajt, il-ġestjoni tal-proġett, u l-integrazzjoni ta 'WordPress.",
    "Deepglot signs every delivery with a timestamp and HMAC signature.": "Deepglot jiffirma kull konsenja b'timestamp u firma HMAC.",
    "Deepglot support is available Monday to Friday from 9 a.m. to 5 p.m.": "L-appoġġ Deepglot huwa disponibbli mit-Tnejn sal-Ġimgħa mid-9 a.m. sal-5 p.m.",
    "Deepglot translates your WordPress content automatically with AI at a fraction of the usual cost. Your translations stay yours.": "Deepglot jittraduċi l-kontenut WordPress tiegħek awtomatikament b'AI bi frazzjoni tal-ispiża tas-soltu. It-traduzzjonijiet tiegħek jibqgħu tiegħek.",
    "Deepglot will continue to send important account, security, and project emails. Optional notification controls will appear once they can be persisted.": "Deepglot se jkompli jibgħat emails importanti dwar kontijiet, sigurtà u proġett. Kontrolli ta' notifika mhux obbligatorji se jidhru ladarba jkunu jistgħu jibqgħu jippersistu.",
    "DeepL translation API. No model id is needed.": "API tat-traduzzjoni DeepL. L-ebda mudell id mhu meħtieġ.",
    "Default: gpt-5-mini for best cost/quality. Pro/flagship models like gpt-5.5 are opt-in.": "Default: gpt-5-mini għall-aħjar spiża/kwalità. Mudelli Pro/flagship bħal gpt-5.5 huma opt-in.",
